Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to see me?\NTo give me a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Empire has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to help protect\Nan entire empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.89,0:00:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be you, and you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what if I fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say the empire...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.19,0:00:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't the only thing that's returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparklriffic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With Cadance putting all her strength\Ninto keeping her spell going,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and me trying to keep an eye\Non signs of trouble in the arctic,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't been able to gather\Nmuch information from the Crystal Ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There are Crystal Ponies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't seem to remember anything\Nbefore King Sombra came to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,History of the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The last page of the book mentioned\Na crystal heart as the fair's centerpiece,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so I used my magic to cut one\Nout of a crystal block.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole purpose of the Crystal Fair\Nis to lift the spirits of the Crystal Ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,so the light within them\Ncan power the Crystal Heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:00:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the empire can be protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we may have\Na problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know it was an actual relic!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.33,0:01:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 3 | Episode 2\NThe Crystal Empire, Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed and Synced by GrayJeager\NFr.Jeager@Gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/GhxBronie\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The empire is under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to find the Crystal Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.45,0:02:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you stay here with Cadance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs you, Shining Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll retrieve the Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been trying to figure out\Nhow I'm meant to pass Celestia's test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Retrieving the Crystal Heart must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is something else you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You and the rest of our friends\Nhave to keep the fair going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? With that thing\Nmoving into the empire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole purpose of the Crystal Fair\Nis to lift the spirits of the Crystal Ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so they can activate the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Crystal Ponies find out King Sombra\Nis trying to take over the empire again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.25,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,their spirits are gonna be\Nanything but lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't matter if I find the Crystal Heart.\NThey won't be able to make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to keep them happy\Nhere at the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the fair going and\Nthe Crystal Ponies' spirits high.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Done and done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilie,\Nbe careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just found out they're offering\Nface painting for the little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do that.\NTwilight's doing what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He... really... loves\Ngetting his face painted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants a flugelhorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a flugelhorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else wants a flugelhorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a flugelhorn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't. I have to retrieve\Nthe Crystal Heart by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I promise\NI won't lift a claw to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a claw, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might know where\NKing Sombra hid the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The king would've been\Ncounting on the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,that nopony would dare\Ncome looking for it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd've been too afraid to even try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me both.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you lookin' at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to be actin'\Nlike nothing's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What I mean is,\Nmaybe you should let me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,keep the Crystal Ponies away\Nfrom the fake heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,while you show off\Nyour joustin' skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing my awesomeness does have a way\Nof putting ponies into a pretty good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Knight Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's showtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How are y'all feelin'?\NHavin' a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The best I've had\Nin over a thousand years!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good! Gotta renew\Nthat spirit of love and unity
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're gonna power up\Nthat Crystal Heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure would like to see it\Nbefore the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I hear ya, but,\Nuh... phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gettin' a little toasty out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet you'd like to cool off\Nwith a little Crystal Empire nectar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you tried\Nthe Crystal Empire fritters yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Made from a traditional\NCrystal Empire recipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna love 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear there's a joustin' match\Nabout to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna miss that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight... these Crystal Ponies\Nare more curious than a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be here somewhere.\NIt's just gotta be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.98,0:06:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a claw, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Celestia's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the empire is filled\Nwith hope and love,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}those things are reflected\Nacross all of Equestria.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If hatred and fear take hold...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- What? Did you find it?!\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this isn't\NKing Sombra's castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this where he lived\Nwhen he was in power?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It is. But it didn't look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you learn to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a little trick\NCelestia taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see what's down there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. I can't even tell\Nhow far down this goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Spike?\N- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes... crystals... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good! Cadance's magic\Nmust be fading faster than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I think it's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!\NI opened the door and--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.36,0:09:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter to me.\NYou failed the test, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand! The test--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only will you not move on\Nto the next level of your studies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't continue your studies at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't say anything about\Nno longer being your student if I failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what do I do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Twilight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Twilight?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Twiliiiight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you told me to stay up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but you were down here\Nfor such a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and you weren't answering\Nand I got worried so I came down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were just\Nstaring at that wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I was calling your name, but I couldn't\Nseem to get your attention, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you looking at?\NI mean... it's just a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I get...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't wanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Twilight, don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sombra's dark magic.\NA doorway that leads to your worst fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We were home... you told me\Nyou didn't need me any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sending me away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A fear that will never come to pass.\NI'm never gonna send you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not gonna fail my test!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.45,0:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots and lots of stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you should come\Nwith me this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo, knight Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there...\Nsomepony else who could...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,take over the jousting demonstration\Nwith you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The fate of an entire empire rests on us\Nshowing these ponies a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But, y'know,\Nif that isn't important to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay,\NI'll take it easy on you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But not too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a reputation to maintain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What if this is just more of his magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He makes a door that links\Nto your worst nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,why not a staircase\Nthat goes on forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I am running out of weaving materials\Nfor the traditional crafts booths!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just made a hat out of\Nthree pieces of hay and a drinking straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it work. But still!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta do everything we can\Nto keep this thing goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess isn't lookin' so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can imagine her magic\Nis gonna last much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These ponies are gonna power up\Nthat Crystal Heart when the time comes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and we won't be needin'\Nher magic anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope that time comes soon!\NEven I can't keep this party going forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the Crystal Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- The real one is--\N- On its way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to say 'being polished'\Nto buy us some more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crystal Heart... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually studied gravity spells,\Nthinking it might be on our test!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out I was prepared for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heart...\Nwhere's the Crystal--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! It rolled over to me\Nwhen you dropped it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can move, just not toward me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have been so foolish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just so eager to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when I saw what\Nwas going on outside, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get out of there, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be the one who brings\Nthe Crystal Heart to Princess Cadance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't,\Nyou'll fail Celestia's test!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sombra is already attacking\Nthe Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He could reach the Crystal Ponies\Nat any moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,reach Princess Cadance,\Nmy brother, my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There may not be enough time for me\Nto find a way to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:16:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be the one\Nto bring the Crystal Heart to the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? But Twilight--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't y'all worry\Nyour pretty little crystal heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Crystal Heart\Nwill be here any second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if they believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know if I believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's back! I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sombra...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My crystal slaves... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey! Up here!\N- Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the Crystal Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is mine! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Spikey-Wikey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold! The Crystal Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Heart has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the light and love within you\Nto ensure that King Sombra does not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?\NNo... No! Stop! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I do so wish it was permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see how\Nmy mane just absolutely sparkled?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But... good things are better\Nwhen they're a rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta stop saving my rump like this,\Nit's starting to get embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't me who saved you in the end.\NIt was Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a test.\NMaybe she'll let you retake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think she's gonna\Ngive me a new test.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it together, buddy...\Ngotta stay strong... for Twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it had been me\Nwho ultimately made it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight,\Nas I understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike brought Princess Cadance\Nthe Crystal Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because you weren't sure how quickly\Nyou could find a way to escape the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't willing to risk the future\Nof the citizens of the Crystal Empire
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in an effort to guarantee your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Far better that I have a student who\Nunderstands the meaning of self-sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.35,0:20:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,than one who only looks out\Nfor her own best interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's totally gonna lose it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it together, buddy...\Ngotta stay strong... for Twilight...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were prepared to do your best {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Had what it takes to pass the test {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All those doubts you can dismiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turns out\Nyou were prepared for this! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You clearly have just what it takes {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To pass the test with such high stakes {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We knew for sure you would prevail {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since when does\NTwilight Sparkle ever fail? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All those doubts that you can dismiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trust yourself and you cannot miss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turns out you were {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turns out I was {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turns out you were {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turns out I was {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Turns out you were prepared for this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I knew everything\Nwas gonna be fine.
